posting_body: ['Welcome to Miro', 'Miro reflects the dynamic, multi-faceted character of contemporary life.', 'Start your day with a boost of energy at the fitness center, hone in on work from the comfortable co-working lounges, and wrap up the evening soaking up tranquility from the rooftop sky deck.', 'Come home to the perfect blend of easy relaxation, bold design, and quality finishes.', 'Live beyond your expectations.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Exclusive Rooftop Demonstration Kitchen', 'Yoga Studio', 'Billiards Table', 'Capacious Closets', 'Rooftop Deck', 'Smart Climate Control System', 'Complimentary Wi-Fi Available in all Amenities', 'Rooftop Sunset and Sky Lounges NOW OPEN', 'Firepits', 'Contemporary European Cabinetry', 'Controlled Access', 'Concrete Wall and Column Accents', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
